subject: College Athletics
Basketball
lead_paragraph: A. J. Abrams had 17 points and No. 6 Texas turned in another strong defensive effort in a 68-50 victory over St. Joseph’s in the opening round of the EA Sports Maui Invitational in Lahaina, Hawaii. In the semifinals, the Longhorns (3-0) will meet No. 8 Notre Dame, which got 21 points from Tory Jackson in pounding Indiana, 88-50.
